Package com.thebluealliance.api.v3.models

Contains the models represented by JSON data from The Blue Alliance API.

See: Description

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Award
    A Award object represents an award won at a FIRST Robotics Competition event and its associated descriptors.
    District
    A District object represents a district for a particular year
    DistrictRanking
    Rank of a Team in a district.
    EliminationAlliance
    Represents an alliance of teams during the elimination tournament
    Event
    Represents a FIRST Robotics Competition event and its related descriptors
    EventDistrictPoints
    Represents all district points accumulated at an event
    EventPoints
    Holds district point contributions and breakdown for a team at an event
    EventRankings
    Represents event rankings and tiebreaker information for an event
    Match  
    MatchScoreBreakdown2018Alliance  
    MatchScoreBreakdown2019Allliance  
    Media
    Contains a reference for most any media associated with a team or event on TBA.
    OPRs
    Contains OPR, DPR, and CCWM for teams at the event.
    Ranking
    Represents the ranking of a team at an event
    Robot
    Represents a particular robot in FIRST Robotics Competition
    ScoreBreakdown  
    SimpleEvent
    Shortform representation of a FIRST Robotics Competition event
    SimpleMatch
    Shortform representation of a FIRST Robotics Competition match
    SimpleTeam
    Shortform representation of a FIRST Robotics Competition team
    Team
    Represents a FIRST Robotics Competition team
    TeamEventStatus
    Represents a team's status during an event
    WLTRecord
    A Win-Loss-Tie record for a team, or an alliance.
